, when the picture became more fragmented."],"variants":[]},{"name":"II","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["‘Loving’."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When William II FitzHerbert 2nd Lord of Norbury was born before 1150, in Norbury, Derbyshire, England, his father, William FitzHerbert 1st Lord of Norbury, was 45 and his mother, Alice of Gloucester, was 13. He had at least 1 son with Lucy of Gloucester. He died in 1204, in his hometown."},"et":{"before 1150–1204":"enne 1150–1204","1150–1204":"1150–1204","1162–Female":"1162–Surnud","1136–1220":"1136–1220","1170–Male":"1170–Surnud","1105–Male":"1105–Surnud","1204":"1204","1105":"1105","1136":"1136","1220":"1220","before 1150":"enne 1150","1162":"1162","before 1170":"enne 1170","1150":"1150","1170":"1170","Norbury, Derbyshire, England":"Norbury, Derbyshire, England","Norbury, Derbyshire, England, United Kingdom":"Norbury, Derbyshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"before 1150–1204":"ennen vuotta 1150–1204","1150–1204":"1150–1204","1162–Female":"1162–Kuollut","1136–1220":"1136–1220","1170–Male":"1170–Kuollut","1105–Male":"1105–Kuollut","1204":"1204","1105":"1105","1136":"1136","1220":"1220","before 1150":"ennen vuotta 1150","1162":"1162","before 1170":"ennen vuotta 1170","1150":"1150","1170":"1170","Norbury, Derbyshire, England":"Norbury, Derbyshire, England","Norbury, Derbyshire, England, United Kingdom":"Norbury, Derbyshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"before 1150–1204":"avant 1150–1204","1150–1204":"1150–1204","1162–Female":"1162–Décédée","1136–1220":"1136–1220","1170–Male":"1170–Décédé","1105–Male":"1105–Décédé","1204":"1204","1105":"1105","1136":"1136","1220":"1220","before 1150":"avant 1150","1162":"1162","before 1170":"avant 1170","1150":"1150","1170":"1170","Norbury, Derbyshire, England":"Norbury, Derbyshire, Angleterre","Norbury, Derbyshire, England, United Kingdom":"Norbury, Derbyshire, Angleterre, Royaume